curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/7173' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM13005H1", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM13005H1 is a low noise amplifier (LNA) for LTE  high band receiver applications. The device features low  noise figure and high linearity over a supply voltage  range from 1.5V to 3.6V. Low noise figure improves the  sensitivity of the SGM13005H1, and high linearity  enables the device to provide better immunity to  interference signals.  No external DC blocking capacitors are required on the  RF paths as long as no external DC voltage is applied,  which can save PCB area and cost.  The SGM13005H1 is available in a Green UTDFN-  1.1×0.7-6L package.    "}'
